            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="274025431">
            山顶还有一个寺庙，在这里几乎收不到信号，与世隔绝
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_273853607" data-seq="273853677" data-pid="273853607" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="3497">
