            <div data-seq="274460577" data-index="2" class="article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem">
                <h2 class="t9"><span class="_j_anchor">如果不告诉你这是公路，你会以为这是赛道</span></h2>
            </div>
            <div  class="add_video _j_seqitem " data-vid="612578" data-seq="274467361" data-url="E3D57273001CF3519C33DC5901307461" data-type="0" data-ready="1">
    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="274460616">
            ▲&nbsp;<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a><a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/13541.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="房山" target="_blank">房山</a>、<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11319.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="怀柔" target="_blank">怀柔</a>等地航拍视频&nbsp;拍摄时间17年9月<br />
<br />
在<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>游玩的这些地方，<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11319.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="怀柔" target="_blank">怀柔</a>、<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/13541.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="房山" target="_blank">房山</a>、<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/13380.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="门头沟" target="_blank">门头沟</a>是我常去的地方<br />
是因这些地方的公路一路上都是让人流连忘返的景色<br />
在没有接触无人机的时候，己经不知道走了多少次<br />
玩起了无人机立刻就去从走这些地方再看看这片大地，透过无人机的镜头从新认识了一下这些地方
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_274460200" data-seq="274460202" data-pid="274460200" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8086315/274460200.html">
